      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six. This example features a pristine Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a dual-VANOS overhaul. The rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. Finished in immaculate Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the vehicle retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and limited-slip differential, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are renowned for. A zero-compromise, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
