      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman, finished in timeless GT Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and represents the pinnacle of its class. The exterior paint remains in flawless condition, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and a full-front paint protection film with zero rock chips or road rash. Inside, the black leather interior retains its factory-fresh scent and original matte finish; there is absolutely no bolster wear, creasing, or sun damage to the dashboard. Every switch and dial operates with crisp, mechanical precision. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized Porsche centers. It comes complete with both original keys, all owner's manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. For the buyer who demands a 'time capsule' experience, this vehicle is truly without peer.",
